Select your running instance.

Copy Public IPv4 address.

Use that IP in SSH and browser.


STEP 37: If project upload fails

From Ubuntu PC terminal:

cd ~/Downloads
ls

Make sure these are present:

website-key.pem
ecommerce-mern

Then upload again:

scp -i website-key.pem -r ecommerce-mern ubuntu@YOUR_EC2_PUBLIC_IP:/home/ubuntu/


STEP 38: If port 5000 is already in use on EC2

Check process:

sudo lsof -i :5000

Kill old process if needed:

sudo kill -9 PID

Then restart app:

